[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "果ての大陸へ渡るため、\nお二人の力を貸していただけないでしょうか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00919",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "集めた九偉人図に、「九人の偉人」の助けがいるって\n書いてあったのよ。私たち九偉人のことでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00920",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "負けた相手に力を貸すのは嫌だろうけど、\nそこをなんとか――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00921",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "って、ちょっと！\nお二人さん？　聞いてます！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00922",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "……はぁ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00923",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00924",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……あの、どこか具合でも悪いんでしょうか。\n私の錬金術でよければ、薬を――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00925",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "多分違うよ、二人とも最近ずっとこんな感じだから。\n特にヘルトのほう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00926",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "聞こえてるはずなのに、何も反応がなくて……\n抵抗したり暴れられるよりはぜんぜんいいんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00927",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……確かに。なんか魂が抜けているみたい。\nどうしてこんなことになってるのかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00928",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者、ゼロはここにおるぞ、兄者ぁ\n",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00929",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "ぬあああ、どうしてしまったんじゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00930",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "うぬらの言葉はともかく、かわいい妹たる我の言葉を\n兄者が無視するはずがないのじゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00931",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "……とまあ、ゼロの話にあるように、今のヘルトには\nゼロの言葉すら届いていないみたいなんだよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00932",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ゼロが大人しいのはヘルトの元気がないから。\nつまるところ、ヘルトの様子がおかしすぎるってわけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00933",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ふーん？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00934",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "おーい、ヘルトおにいちゃーん。ヘル兄。\n兄様。あにい。ちょっと話があるんだけどー……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00935",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ダメだね、反応がない。\nまるでしかばねのようっすわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00936",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "気味の悪いことを言うでない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00937",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あの、ヘルトさん！　少しでいいので、\nお話を聞いていただけませんか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00938",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ちょっとなんか本当に魂抜けてない？\nまったく反応がなくて、元敵とはいえ心配になるわ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00939",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ちなみにゼロにも、果ての大陸に向けて\n力を貸してほしいんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00940",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者が力を貸すと言うのなら、我も貸してやろう。\n我はうぬらに敗北したのじゃからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00941",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、ありがとうございます！　ゼロさん！\nよろしくお願いします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00942",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "それはいいから、兄者をなんとかせい。我は悲しい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00943",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うーん、なんとかしたいけど、今日ヘルトに話を\n聞いてもらうのは、ムリそうっすね～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00944",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "果ての大陸へ渡るために、\n九偉人全員に協力をお願いしたいんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00945",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それじゃあ、話を聞いてもらえるくらいに\nヘルトを元気づけなきゃダメね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00946",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うーん？　元気とか、そういう問題なのか……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00947",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリア、何か考えがあるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00948",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ。なんだかんだ自分のお兄ちゃんのことだしね。\n私がなんとかするわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00949",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "こういうときは、\n美味しいご飯をお腹いっぱい食べるのが一番よ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00950",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "記憶を失う前の私が自分を見失った時も、\nフロッケたち家族のご飯で正気を取り戻したらしいし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00951",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "美味しいご飯か……\nそれはまあ、一理あるかも？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00952",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "でしょ？　それに、果ての大陸へ向けて\n九偉人みんなの結束を固めたいとも思っていたし――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00953",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "よし、決めた！　九偉人の一人として！\n九偉人、家族会を開催するわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00954",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]